    "title": "Testing localizations when running your app"
  },
  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "Overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "After you import localizations that contain the translated strings and resources",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "adapted for the culture and region, test each localization in your running app by",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "choosing the language and region in the Run scheme. You can also automate testing",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "of localizations using continuous integration by choosing a localization when you",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "create a bot.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Select-a-language-and-region-in-the-scheme",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Select a language and region in the scheme",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "In Xcode, choose Product > Scheme > Edit Scheme. In the sheet that appears, select",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "the Run scheme action in the left column, and click Options on the right. Choose",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "the language from the App Language pop-up menu and choose a region from the App Region",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "pop-up menu:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "header": "row",
          "rows": [
            [
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Region",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Description",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            ],
            [
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "System Region",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "The operating system region settings.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            ],
            [
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "[Development Region]",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "The region that you’re developing the app in (the second menu item).",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            ],
            [
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "[Region]",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "A specific region. Choose a region from a continent submenu.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            ]
          ],
          "type": "table"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Click Close in the sheet and click the Run button in the toolbar.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Choose-the-language-and-region-for-a-bot",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Choose the language and region for a bot",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You can test the languages and regions you support systematically using continuous",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "integration with a bot. In Xcode, from the Language and Region action pop-up menus",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "in the bot configuration sheet, you can choose either a localization, pseudolanguage,",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "or Use Scheme Settings. If you choose Use Scheme Settings from the Language menu,",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "the bot uses the localization settings you choose from the App Language and App Region",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "pop-up menus in the scheme editor.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "identifier": "testing-localizations-when-running-your-app-1",
              "type": "image"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Click Next in the sheet to complete the bot configuration.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "For details on creating bots, see ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "https://help.apple.com/xcode/mac/current/#/dev466720061",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "in Xcode Help.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
